pportunities  the firm employs a network of almost  people with headquarters in new york and additional offices in buenos aires hong kong jakarta kuala lumpur lima london montevideo new delhi shanghai singapore and são paulo  trg is differentiated by its ability to leverage its capabilities to offer both traditional forms of exposure to emerging markets as well as innovative solutions customized for various types of investors  the firm places a strong emphasis on partnering with its investors and delivering an institutional level of client service  trgs asset management services are supported by a comprehensive infrastructure in risk management finance and accounting legal and compliance global operations marketing investor relations and information technology  trg is a registered investment adviser with the united states securities and exchange commission sec  trg has completed a ssae  type ii audit and an isae  audit and is a signatory of the hedge fund standards board hfsb established and managed by trg subsidiaries including arch capital management co ltd a owned subsidiary of trg management lp and capital advisors partners asia ltd a majority owned subsidiary of trg management lp         the rohatyn group terms of use privacy policy microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to not delete browsing history on exit instructions for enabling cookies and configuring your browsing history may be available in your browsers settings privacy or help documentation sign in hold on… we’re sorry but this didn’t work you can’t turn off personalized ads right now because your browser is currently blocking thirdparty cookies we can help you fix this issue let’s get started depending on what browser you use open options or settings make sure that thirdparty cookies are not blocked anymore to find out how search your browser’